#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"### Actions \n"
"**Multiattack.** The bear makes two attacks: one with its bite and one with "
"its claws.    \n"
"**Bite.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +5 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ "
"8 (1d8 + 4) piercing damage.    \n"
"**Claws.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +5 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ "
"11 (2d6 + 4) slashing damage.\n"
